<h2>Motivation</h2>
<ul class="slide">
   <li>Profile of target users:
       <ul class="sub1">
          <li>Less technical competence</li>
          <li>Not able to install upstream programs with acceptable
              effort</li>
          <li>No interest in administration</li>
          <li>Interest in defined subset of available free
              software</li>
          <li>Need for easy usage</li>
          <li>Defined security profile</li>
       </ul>
   </li>
   <li>Other possible projects:
       <ul class="sub1">
         <li>Authorities</li>
         <li>Office</li>
         <li>Enterprise / accounting</li>
         <li>???</li>
       </ul>
   </li>
</ul>
  </td>
 </tr><tr>
