<h2>General menu rewrite</h2>
<ul class="slide">
   <li>Currently Debian menu system is completely rewritten</li>
   <li>Debian packages update general menu after installation
       automatically</li>
   <li>Key features like user roles and translation will be added</li>
   <li>Plan: Meta packages contain role specific menu entries which
       are updated on a per user basis</li>
   <li>Enabling clean administration of multi user systems</li>
</ul>
